    <description>Sends a Slack alert to the owner of an opportunity that&apos;s hit 31 days without any sales touchpoint. 
10/16/23 - Tweak this flow to make 31 days the entry criteria
3/13/26 - DM- updated flow to 7 day entry criteria with updated sales neglected criteria
3/19/26 - DM - added in criteria that contact is not in &apos;Sales - Keep Warm&apos; cadence</description>
