    <textTemplates>
        <description>Template of message to be sent via Slack to opportunity owner and their manager</description>
        <name>textT_SlackOpportunityReminder</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>true</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>Hello {!$Record.Owner.Name}, it has been 7 days since the last touchpoint with the prospect from opportunity &lt;https://brightwheel1.my.salesforce.com/{!$Record.Id}|{!$Record.Name}&gt;. The last sales activity is showing {!$Record.Sales_Last_Contacted__c}. 

Please either reach out to them or mark the opportunity as Lost. If there&apos;s no action in the next 7 days, the opportunity will automatically go &apos;Closed Lost - Neglected.&apos; Thanks!</text>
